{"tid":676934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟你地識分「質素」同「質量」未？","createTime":"2018-05-24T18:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T11:46:53.000Z","uid":26418,"like":92,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ba25a5c8814634679ee6ced24c036740faaeaa","tid":676934,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:58:25.000Z","msg":"質素=quality<br />\n質量=mass<br />\n<br />\n兩個字有幾難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論政府定傳媒都愈黎愈鍾意講「施工質量」「工程質量」「食品質量」<br />\n唯一仲可以聽到「質素」就只係得番「空氣質素健康指數」呢個<br />\n<br />\n究竟係因為你地冇讀過物理，唔知質量係乜？<br />\n定更多可能係溫水煮蛙咁俾人洗哂腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔覺得 質量=quality有問題？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/73964/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/73964/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n可能十年後會有人開POST「正字撚點解釋香港人2016年已經講充值?」 <br />\n<br />\n會唔會唔洗十年後..已經俾人屌返轉頭 做乜講質素唔講質量 質量先多人講 質量先係解quality <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264a5e79efb697f83221a6f1733116c721637ab9","tid":676934,"uid":151774,"like":1,"dislike":47,"score":-46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:59:43.000Z","msg":"有質量=有質素"},{"pid":"a5378b58f0d4a8ea872ae19664e1421af37b26df","tid":676934,"uid":26418,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:06:53.000Z","msg":"真係癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有乜「安全質量」「食水質量」<br />\n<br />\n例子：<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201601/08/P201601080721.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201601%2F08%2FP201601080721.htm&d=Rg7HdfaKKD%2F56qGoPWq68tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=afe459