br />\n有貨=有質素=有料"},{"pid":"2fd0b573f1e43803b362d5fd38ae3517c4c9a357","tid":676934,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"因為支那製造除咗quality 有問題，連個quantity都出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷工減料，正正經經設計畫圖，根本只有quality都出錯，製造良率唔夠。係技術嘅問題<br />\n但依家支那人係會唔跟圖則，偷工減料，連個量都可以唔跟<br />\n所以先會用「質量」嚟代表埋個量嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常用料嘅量有數得計，點會因為個量唔夠而出錯？"},{"pid":"3ff8a3d8d1cc63c364c75a1c1abcafdd7e7ee454","tid":676934,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T11:00:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為支那製造除咗quality 有問題，連個quantity都出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷工減料，正正經經設計畫圖，根本只有quality<span style=\"color: red;\">會</span>出錯，製造良率唔夠。係技術嘅問題<br />\n但依家支那人係會唔跟圖則，偷工減料，連個量都可以唔跟<br />\n所以先會用「質量」嚟代表埋個量嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常用料嘅量有數得計，點會因為個量唔夠而出錯？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"31907858d83bc925e375c143e676f05e995aef84","tid":676934,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"最簡單直接<br />\n話 質量 係 質素加數量 嘛<br />\n啫係quality 加quantity 啦<br />\n但從來只會做quality control <br />\n冇人會做quantity control<br />\n形容個嘢嘅 可靠程度 要用quality +quantity 本身就係好低質嘅世界先會有嘅邏輯"},{"pid":"9e2c8237b268781a4be2b2794412dc05caa6bbed","tid":676934,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d3c9a92220c8863f84c60ec8fa02aff82b08d7f","tid":676934,"uid":683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"三國個陣有一本書叫《人物誌》，入邊有一句係咁樣既<br />\n<br />\n「凡人之質量，中和最貴矣」<br />\n<br />\n想問下樓主，呢句係咪解普通人既mass係average就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wond